Titolo: Battlefield 2042

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Battlefield 2042 is a first-person shooter game developed by DICE and published by Electronic Arts. It is the seventeenth installment in the Battlefield series, and was released in 2021 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X and S. Unlike previous games in the series, Battlefield 2042 is solely multiplayer and does not have a single-player campaign. It also features support for cross-platform play, a first in the series. Upon release, Battlefield 2042 received mixed reviews from critics and a negative reception from players.



Genere: First-person shooter

Valutazione: 65
